brm_binom <- brm(germination | trials(size) ~ solar + nutrition, family = binomial(), 
    data = df, seed = 1, chains = 4, iter = 2000, warmup = 1000, thin = 1, prior = c(set_prior("", 
        class = "Intercept")))

pred_mat <- pred_df %>% mutate(Intercept = 1) %>% select("Intercept", "solarsunshine", 
    "nutrition") %>% as.matrix

mcmc_bx <- pred_mat %*% t(beta_mat)

make_bx_summary <- function(bx) {
    pred_zs <- lapply(1:nrow(bx), function(i) {
        matrow <- bx[i, ]
        c(mean(matrow), quantile(matrow, probs = c(0.005, 0.025, 0.1, 0.5, 0.9, 
            0.975, 0.995))) %>% setNames(nm = c("mean", "p0.5", "p2.5", "p10", 
            "p50", "p90", "p97.5", "p99.5"))
    }) %>% do.call(bind_rows, .)
    pred_zs
}

bayes_zs <- make_bx_summary(mcmc_bx)
bayes_probs <- 1/(1 + exp(-bayes_zs))
bayes_nums <- 10 * bayes_probs

pred_mcmc_df <- bind_cols(pred_df, bayes_nums)

pred_mcmc_df %>% ggplot() + geom_line(aes(x = nutrition, y = mean, color = solar), 
    size = 1) + geom_ribbon(aes(x = nutrition, ymin = p2.5, ymax = p97.5, fill = solar), 
    alpha = 0.5) + geom_point(data = df, aes(x = nutrition, y = germination, 
    color = solar, shape = solar), size = 2) + scale_color_lancet() + scale_fill_lancet() + 
    theme_light(base_size = 14, base_line_size = 1.5, base_rect_size = 0.5) + 
    theme(legend.position = c(0.01, 0.98), legend.justification = c(0, 1), legend.background = element_rect(size = 1, 
        color = "gray70"))

make_pred <- function(bx, base_size, n_generation) {
    pred_zs <- lapply(1:nrow(bx), function(i) {
        matrow <- bx[i, ]
        pred_probs <- 1/(1 + exp(-matrow))
        pred_nums <- sapply(pred_probs, function(p) {
            rbinom(size = base_size, n = n_generation, prob = p)
        }) %>% as.vector
        
        c(mean(pred_nums), quantile(pred_nums, probs = c(0.005, 0.025, 0.1, 
            0.5, 0.9, 0.975, 0.995))) %>% setNames(nm = c("mean", "p0.5", "p2.5", 
            "p10", "p50", "p90", "p97.5", "p99.5"))
    }) %>% do.call(bind_rows, .)
}

pred_result <- make_pred(mcmc_bx, base_size = 10, n_generation = 10)
bind_cols(pred_df, pred_result) %>% ggplot() + geom_line(aes(x = nutrition, 
    y = p50, color = solar), size = 1) + geom_ribbon(aes(x = nutrition, ymin = p0.5, 
    ymax = p99.5, fill = solar), alpha = 0.5) + geom_point(data = df, aes(x = nutrition, 
    y = germination, color = solar, shape = solar), size = 2) + theme_light(base_size = 14, 
    base_line_size = 1.5, base_rect_size = 0.5) + scale_color_lancet() + scale_fill_lancet() + 
    theme(legend.position = c(0.01, 0.99), legend.justification = c(0, 1), legend.background = element_rect(color = "gray70", 
        size = 1))
